<L>__{exterior base trail #2 day}
<A>__{mike and sheryl reach a small clearing. there are a number of signs pointing toward different trails. (donner trail, willow creek bridge, timber falls, etc.) sheryl grabs the map and some water. mike swigs some water, munches on trail mix, takes a peek in the guidebook.}
