<D>__{...willow creek bridge. i think sam only knows those two trails. well. between those, i'd pick donner trail. willow creek will shoot you to the top, but there's not as much to see. donner weaves through peddler's point, it's a better hike and prettier all around view.}
<C>__{sheryl}
<P>__{(to mike)}
<D>__{what do you think?}
<A>__{then, she notices a ring on sheryl's finger.}
